main event: A ground visual observation of 4 unidentified objects near Ukiah, California, on 25 September 1962.
interesting points: The observation lasted for 5 minutes, The observer reported a bright flash near the horizon, The objects were noted to have a straight course, Possible explanations included balloon, satellite, missile, and astronomical matter, The sighting was reported by a reliable eyewitness.
witness description: A reliable military observer from the 563 AEW&C SQ.
